com.bigdata.rdf.sail.model

Class RunningQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.rdf.sail.model.RunningQuery

  • public class RunningQuery
extends Object
    Metadata about running BigdataRDFContext.AbstractQueryTasks (this includes both queries and update requests). Used to serialize the results for the REST interface in JSON, XML, etc.
